milestones.description: Gavaskar has scored 4 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for IND breaking Vengsarkar's record
Ian Botham has become the top wicket-taker for ENG in ODIs with 46 wickets, going past Chris Old's 45
Gavaskar and Sandeep Patil's 76-run partnership is IND's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 65 between Chauhan and Yashpal Sharma
